<item>
            <title>[LU-9853] mount.lustre noisy on mount</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9853</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It seems that lately mount.lustre is very chatyy, every time I use it I have it complain that:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;mount.lustre FATAL: unhandled/unloaded fs type 0 &apos;ext3&apos;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is using ldiskfs and I believe zfs too.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;E.g. when runing replay* or recovery* tests every mount attempt is generating this message.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
